node.title: Terence Kelly pleads guilty to abducting four-year-old Cleo Smith
node.description: Cleo Smith was missing for 18 days before being found by police.
node.content: ["Terence Kelly has pleaded guilty to the abduction of four-year-old Cleo Smith from a Western Australia campsite.\u00a0", "Kelly admitted his guilt when he appeared in Carnarvon Magistrates Court on Monday morning via video link from the maximum-security Casuarina Prison in Perth.", "The four-year-old girl vanished while on a family camping trip in the outback for 18 days.\u00a0Police received a tip that led them to a house in Carnarvon where they found Cleo in a bedroom.", "More to come.\u00a0"]
